# ==============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# Security Reminders:
# 1. Never commit actual terraform.tfvars files to version control
# 2. Use terraform.tfvars.example for documentation
# 3. Store sensitive values in secure secret management systems
# 4. Use .tfvars files locally and in CI/CD pipelines only
# 5. Regularly audit .gitignore to ensure no sensitive files are tracked
#
# Best Practices:
# 1. Use remote state backends for team collaboration
# 2. Implement state locking to prevent concurrent modifications
# 3. Use versioned modules for reusability
# 4. Document infrastructure changes in commit messages
# 5. Use pre-commit hooks to validate Terraform code
#
# ==============================================================================